        <p>
          The Presenter touch walls have either chemically strengthened or tempered-glass tops and the chassis is made 
          out of aircraft-grade aluminum. The Presenters have exceptional build-quality and are perfect for public spaces 
          and other demanding environments.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
